'''Sanfew''' is the leader of the druids and resides in [[Taverley]], on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of [[Jatix's Herblore Shop]]. He plays a part in several quests, including [[Druidic Ritual]], [[Eadgar's Ruse]], and [[One Small Favour]].

==[[Goutweed]] Exchange==
Sanfew will exchange goutweed for a clean [[herb]].

